</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"MicroprocessorandInterfacing-=E2=9C=85Summary.3">=E2=9C=85 <stron=
g>Summary</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Assemblers:</strong> Convert human-readable assembly code into m=
achine code.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Debuggers:</strong> Help trace, test, and fix programs.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Development Systems:</strong> Provide a complete programming env=
ironment for writing, testing, and debugging microprocessor programs.</p></=
li>
</ul>
