<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Device</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Interface Concept</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Keyboard Matrix</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Rows and columns scanned via I/O ports; key press detected by row-column=
 intersection</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>LCD/7-Segment Display</strong></p></td>
