<p>Data/Control lines connected to ports; CPU sends ASCII/data codes to dis=
play</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Printer</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Handshake lines for busy/ready; data transferred via parallel port</p></=
td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Stepper Motor</strong></p></td>
