<p>Analog input converted to digital; CPU reads digital value via port or i=
nterrupt</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>D/A Converter</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Digital data from CPU converted to analog signal for actuator control</p=
></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
